{"tid":306000,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"條女係痴線/有精神病既入一入黎","createTime":"2017-07-02T07:23:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-24T16:20:38.000Z","uid":54581,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d2734c35b26fd171f043eadea338857375d8cb66","tid":306000,"uid":54581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T07:23:39.000Z","msg":"你地點頂落去？<br />\n<br />\n講下我case, 我懷疑佢有啲自殘傾向、反社會人格、焦慮症同人格分裂<br />\n<br />\n佢唔發作既時候好好，又cute又叻女 又幾體貼，會咋嗲得黎 同佢又好似男仔frd一樣咁，一齊評論下啲女，etc<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但仆你個街，一發作真係好撚難頂<br />\n每次佢發脾氣/我唔知點樣激嬲佢，佢會block撚晒我所有野.. 有時又會屌我老母，叫我食屎咁<br />\n<br />\n到我發脾氣，駡番佢 佢又會講啲野咒自己，話我再駡佢佢就會點點點，咁逼我停口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有時我想冷戰，大家冷靜下，佢又會話我唔彩佢，問我係咪想分手，問我係咪想睇住佢死... wtf<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好想問下大家，我應唔應該帶佢睇醫生<br />\n因為佢發脾氣同唔發脾氣知陣真係好撚極端<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d54ca0dd2957ba6eb2e92d9501f5d844a0db8e9","tid":306000,"uid":54581,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T07:28:19.000Z","msg":"不過佢進步左啲<br />\n<br />\n之前佢會拎把蛟剪行住佢自己 趕我出房<br />\n<br />\n連氹都唔俾我氹"},{"pid":"1e41fdf1fd9c4dd3fca84830023b4b5978ba911e","tid":306000,"uid":54581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T07:34:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f5c2a75ac72ca48c09820261aa711a7e7e9a6fc","tid":306000,"uid":42694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T07:36:02.000Z","msg":"想繼續定中飛先？"},{"pid":"47b8c9b5b8a9a274c48abddeba6eba7799f9882d","tid":306000,"uid":82958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T07:36:19.000Z","msg":"Me"},{"pid":"818518186298dacabbb0594e582154cc727f3f2a","tid":306000,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T07:37:02.000Z","msg":"hi"},{"pid":"7e24464ddd343cdc64b5e00d61bacd142ba9a29a","tid":306000,"uid":69898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T07:40:16.000Z","msg":"帶佢睇醫生啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申，女朋友睇完醫生好番好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cc68f177e54036f5dee1e2e56077a35cd4cfc54","tid":306000,"uid":54581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T07:42:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想繼續定中飛先？</blockquote><br />\n想繼續先上黎問<br />\n<br />\n但有時變到好壓抑自己，驚一踩到佢條尾又有排氹<br />\n<br />\n又有時我想打下機，做下野先同佢傾電話<br />\n<br />\n佢會唔俾我收線，唔係就重覆做我開頭講既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c3ed5bd600c3d9c068770686606ba5e538d367c","tid":306000,"uid":105400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T07:45:53.000Z","msg":"樓主 加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41379ebc910c03395d9b280f3603656bc4a7aea5","tid":306000,"uid":44243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T07:47:28.000Z","msg":"樓主又撚狗"},{"pid":"4eb95a9127d8b397ef81514f82f7245095eda648","tid":306000,"uid":47480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T07:48:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>不過佢進步左啲<br />\n<br />\n之前佢會拎把蛟剪行住佢自己 趕我出房<br />\n<br />\n連氹都唔俾我氹</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n拎把蛟剪行住佢自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cebfc40a03f686b6d2dd3015fde0a74484a3f83","tid":306000,"uid":41954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T07:50:15.000Z","msg":"捉佢去睇醫生啦"},{"pid":"b3153bfe47a0f8b99069c2398ad98588834ca093","tid":306000,"uid":106375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T07:50:29.000Z","msg":"同佢對鬧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我好清楚佢唔會為左我而自殘"},{"pid":"8d4b192d00f3bdbe9de125203